<li id="cite_note-Why?-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="Judeo-Islamic#cite_ref-Why?_1-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="Judeo-Islamic#cite_ref-Why?_1-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dennis_Prager" title="Dennis Prager">Prager, D</a>; <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_Telushkin" title="Joseph Telushkin">Telushkin, J</a>. <i>Why the Jews?: The Reason for Antisemitism</i>. New York: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simon_%26_Schuster" title="Simon &amp; Schuster">Simon &amp; Schuster</a>, 1983. pp. 110–26.</span>
